            "value": "\"Costal monsters, and monsters that represent a unique connection between fish and bird, are considered Seabreeze monsters. Among them you will find many gulls and flying fish. They (as expected) are mostly found on the coast, and use elements of the salty breeze and costal waves in their attacks.\""
